N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 6.14 - Final determination made by commission

State Regulations

The record of the hearing, together with the memorandum of
the administrative judge and any exceptions or argument duly submitted, shall
be transmitted to the commission for final determination and
order. Notes
